Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.83,0:00:05.90,San,San,0,0,0,,I'm Isogai Sanako, 17 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:08.78,San,San,0,0,0,,Your brother always takes good care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:13.64,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Have we met somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:18.02,San,San,0,0,0,,It is a small city, so we may have passed each other on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:20.13,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,You're really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.13,0:00:22.31,San,San,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:26.88,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,You're so beautiful, yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:29.30,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yet Onii-chan has...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:30.59,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.59,0:00:31.97,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:36.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Good. Mei-chan didn't figure out that she's Sanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:38.04,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm surprised, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:40.82,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell she was my mom for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:34.47,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Get off! Get off of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:37.69,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Please, I'm begging you, so get off of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:39.84,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hey, there's a ghost right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:41.81,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'll tell our mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:15.31,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I still think I've met her somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.31,0:02:16.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.89,0:02:20.18,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Where do you think Sunohara-san is headed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:22.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Maybe some food to start out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:25.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But does he know any classy restaurants?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:28.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey Nagisa. Do you remember what's around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.51,0:02:31.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No... I'm sorry, I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:35.17,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Sa-Sanako-san. Would you be hungry at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:36.33,San,San,0,0,0,,Yes, a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:40.86,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Then there's a place I go to a lot.\NHow about we start by filling our stomachs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:43.97,San,San,0,0,0,,That sounds good. Take me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:46.05,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,This is the place I visit regularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:49.81,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,It's a really nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:51.06,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.43,0:02:53.76,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,My recommendation is the pork cutlet bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:55.52,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I eat it like three times a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:03:00.46,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,It's an expensive store,\Nso average students stay away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:01.73,San,San,0,0,0,,Youhei-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:04.58,San,San,0,0,0,,You regularly eat here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.98,0:03:06.20,San,San,0,0,0,,And only pork cutlet bowls?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:09.44,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Someone like me can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:17.50,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(957.273,415.8)}Episode 3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:17.50,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(960,712.5)}Hearts that do not Converge
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:19.58,San,San,0,0,0,,It's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:21.09,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:23.02,Default,All,0,0,0,,Itadakimasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:25.09,Default,All,0,0,0,,Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:27.78,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,It was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:30.85,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,But the flavoring tasted familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:34.22,San,San,0,0,0,,Eating only pork cutlet bowls is an unbalanced diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:36.77,San,San,0,0,0,,Please try cooking for yourself from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:37.35,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:40.32,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,You're really kind, Sanako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:45.44,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,You're so kind, yet Onii-chan has...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:47.53,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:49.93,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Would you stop that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.94,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Where could they be going next?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:04:00.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I bet to a movie or shopping.\NOne of those standard activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:04.92,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yeah. Who would want to be taken to an arcade right off the bat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:11.94,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,This is horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:12.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:16.22,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san's really into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:27.49,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What's wrong with this thing? I bet it's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:30.53,San,San,0,0,0,,You can't do that, Youhei-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:32.47,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Let's get out of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:34.54,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Let's go to a CD store next.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:36.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,His taste in music is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:39.25,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,It's horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:43.17,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Look, I found it. It's my favorite group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:46.38,San,San,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:49.28,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.49,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,He's completely hopeless today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:56.31,San,San,0,0,0,,It's getting a little dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:58.07,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,The night's just starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:00.31,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Let's go to a place that has some great scenery!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:02.98,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,He still wants to take her around?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:07.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Shouldn't Sanae-san head home soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:10.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. We need to start preparing dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:12.69,Default,Kids,0,0,0,,You're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:11.28,Default-alt,Kids,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:14.62,Default-alt,Kids,0,0,0,,We can't play, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.03,Default,Kids,0,0,0,,I'm not moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.68,Default,Kids,0,0,0,,I said get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.31,Default,Kids,0,0,0,,You're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:20.16,Default,Kids,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:21.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Does it bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:22.20,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:24.11,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'll go stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.19,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:29.04,San,San,0,0,0,,I'll go stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:30.52,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:31.09,San,San,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:34.05,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,That's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:37.06,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Kids grow up through fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.81,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:41.89,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:45.15,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Don't pick on my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:56.91,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Looks like the matter's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:58.79,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Shall we move on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:02.34,San,San,0,0,0,,But um... Something looks wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:05.33,San,San,0,0,0,,Would you wait here for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:15.39,San,San,0,0,0,,It seems they left home on an errand but got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:21.39,San,San,0,0,0,,While the brother was looking for the way home, the sister was bullied by those boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:23.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Lost children, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:26.76,San,San,0,0,0,,I want to find their house for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.90,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,It's fine. They'll find their own way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:31.40,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:32.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Come on now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:37.74,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We should ask their names first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:39.00,San,San,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:41.41,San,San,0,0,0,,What are your names?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:45.45,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,She has a name tag on her clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:49.68,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Great! There's an address written on the back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.67,San,San,0,0,0,,This isn't far from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:53.43,San,San,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:57.26,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad you can go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:07.31,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'm glad it was closer than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:07.94,San,San,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:11.10,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Their parents looked really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:15.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why don't you stop with the attitude and come up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:18.34,San,San,0,0,0,,Are you upset with me, Youhei-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.67,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,No. I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:22.70,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,It was {\i1}our{\i0} date.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:25.29,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Onii-chan, you're still saying something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:30.00,San,San,0,0,0,,Youhei-kun. Please don't be so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:34.10,San,San,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, I'd like to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:34.84,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:40.62,San,San,0,0,0,,It makes me happy that you feel the time we spend together is so important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:43.63,San,San,0,0,0,,But at times, there are things that are more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:46.85,San,San,0,0,0,,Please don't lose sight of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.24,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:00.49,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hello, Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:03.45,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,And a toilet seat cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:05.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You sound really cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:07.31,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Let's go get food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.31,0:08:09.24,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Oh, and a toilet seat cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:10.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll only get food, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.45,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'll have a pork cutlet bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:15.55,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,And a toilet seat cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:17.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You'll upset your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:21.53,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Oh, but Sanae-san told me to watch my diet, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:23.47,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,And a toilet seat cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:28.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Mei-chan was worried about you last night, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:33.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She said you didn't change despite finding such a nice girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.94,0:08:38.98,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Yeah, I should think things over\Nfor Sanae-san's sake, too, like my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.49,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,And a toilet seat cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:43.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're thinking about such a thing for Sanae-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:47.11,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,When I was a kid, I had so many things I wanted to become.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:48.62,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,A soccer player.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:50.90,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,A pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:52.20,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.13,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,A teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:54.50,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Stunning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:55.71,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:08:59.22,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,...a toilet seat cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,They all sound difficult to become.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:04.79,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I can't keep doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:08.01,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Just adding "and a toilet seat cover"\Nat the end ruins any kind of serious talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:10.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then quit doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:13.91,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You're the one who told me to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:14.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:18.47,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Well, I won't get mad at you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:21.61,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,A guy in love has a forgiving heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:23.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're in a really good mood, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:24.67,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:27.12,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,She's supposed to call me after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:30.95,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,It must be that she seriously fell in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:34.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sunohara. Why don't you think about Mei-chan a-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:37.80,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,If I get married to Sanae-san and you to Nagisa-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.43,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,that'd make us brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:42.13,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I look forward to that day, my younger brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.30,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:51.06,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Maybe it had the wrong effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.06,0:09:52.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:54.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That idiot's totally out of his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:02.04,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Mei-chan. Are you waiting for Sunohara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:04.74,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes. You're not with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:06.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He went home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:09.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,He says he shouldn't miss his girl's call.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:12.09,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Gosh, he's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.72,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Would you not bother me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:19.41,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:24.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey! Your sister came all the way to check on you. You shouldn't be saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:28.68,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,When in midst of love, sisters fall out of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:31.05,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Love is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:35.78,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Rather than that, Mei, shouldn't you go home soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:38.05,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'm not going home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:40.89,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,There's something I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:43.30,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Something you have to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:44.99,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Ah, I gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:47.24,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What could they be talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:52.50,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,So basically, checking up on me\Nwas just an excuse to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:56.81,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,She's always loved the city,\Nso she wanted to spend some time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:10:57.83,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:01.62,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:02.72,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:04.38,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,But that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.13,0:11:07.89,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,The person I like is here, so I came to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:10.22,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,P-Person you like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:13.31,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Someone I met the last time I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:16.15,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,He's really mature and teaches me all sorts of fun things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:18.25,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,And he's kind, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:21.10,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,He says I'm cute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:21.90,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Hold on, Mei. {ep 2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:24.88,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Love is amazing, isn't it, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:25.70,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.29,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Who exactly is the-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:28.86,Default-alt,Mei,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to see him after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:30.16,Default-alt,Mei,0,0,0,,So I have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.70,0:11:35.77,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Enjoy your time with her. {ep 2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:38.32,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Mei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:39.61,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:41.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey! You should go after her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:45.92,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, but I shouldn't go in case Sanae-san calls. {ep 2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:48.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you still saying something like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:50.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are you going to do if the guy is some scumbag?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:53.07,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,But love is a person's choice. {ep 2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:06.01,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:09.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry. It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:34.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I understand you're upset with him, but wasn't that a little much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:38.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are you going to do now? You're only complicating things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:41.30,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I don't want to see Onii-chan like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:46.03,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I wanted him to come after me\Nand tell me not to go with a guy like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:49.26,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I didn't mind if he hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.06,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I was ready for him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:54.26,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I wanted him to yell at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:13:03.51,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,When I was little, I was picked on by boys in our neighborhood all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:07.81,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,But Onii-chan was always there to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:12.56,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,When I cried, Onii-chan would always come running to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:15.43,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Saying, "Stop making Mei cry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:20.79,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,It made me really happy and was reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:29.94,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,After starting middle school,\Nhe started to become really good at soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:34.72,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,He was counted on not only by me, but by everyone in the team, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:38.30,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,He's not the brother I used to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:42.99,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,He wouldn't have kept his mouth shut after seeing a girl picked on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:45.93,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,He's supposed to worry about me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:51.43,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san. That girlfriend of Onii-chan's was a fake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:54.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, we knew you'd figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.32,0:13:58.44,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The one who played the role of his girlfriend was my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:01.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sorry we lied to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:03.21,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:07.34,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Gosh, he's so hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:10.14,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Causing so much trouble for everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:12.29,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,No, we never thought of him like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:16.81,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,He's so hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:23.96,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're going on a date with Sunohara again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:27.47,San,San,0,0,0,,Yes. To make up for the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:31.05,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I don't think there's a need to go in disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:35.64,San,San,0,0,0,,I've come to like this outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:38.54,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you all doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:40.02,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,S-Sanae?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:44.38,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Dad, you're amazing! You knew this was Mom instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:46.26,San,San,0,0,0,,Akio-san, this is for-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:47.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:49.53,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Shh! It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:53.19,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What? What are you guys planning on doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:55.50,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,We were practicing theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:56.43,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Theater?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:57.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:15:01.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We wanted Sanae-san to help out with the practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:10.01,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,But man, they're all girls' clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:13.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sanae-san, please go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:12.42,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,What kind of play is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:14.48,San,San,0,0,0,,Excuse me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:15.98,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We're still in the process of coming up with the plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:20.36,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Where did Sanae go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:23.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She probably ran away in embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:26.49,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,She's cute no matter how old she gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:28.70,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,So, what's the story going to be like this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:32.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa's the one coming up with the plot again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:35.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sounds like she's hit a wall,\Nso would you give her some advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.82,0:15:38.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We'll go look for Sanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:40.00,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:45.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,They weren't meeting here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:48.10,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I didn't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:50.78,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I was planning on following Sanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:55.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure we can leave Sanae-san alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:57.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How about we go hang out somewhere, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:02.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you only worry about Sunohara, it'll tire you out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:12.04,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.04,0:16:13.72,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It'd probably look good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:17.37,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I wish you were really my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:19.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you really mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:20.74,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:23.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then try treating me like I'm your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:25.33,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Like you're my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:26.46,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:28.21,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Hey, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:30.93,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:32.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:34.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That was more effective than I'd thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:37.55,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,What are you saying? You're so weird, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:39.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:43.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No more "Onii-chan"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:47.40,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Why? I can't call you "Onii-chan", Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:49.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Actually, don't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:55.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:56.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:17:00.62,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,He's making Mei-chan call him "Onii-chan".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:01.82,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,He's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:03.81,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,He looked really turned on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:05.75,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Oka... Okazaki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:07.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No. There's a reason behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:10.24,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,We didn't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:11.33,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You'll infect us with your idiocy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:12.31,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Run for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:13.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:15.16,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:15.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:16.50,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Don't follow us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:18.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No more "Onii-chan" after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:21.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Actually, I take that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:26.52,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Onii-chan. What should Mei do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:31.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I forbid it!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:34.86,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Wow! There are so many to choose from!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:37.18,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,The city is amazing after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:39.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This isn't really a city, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:41.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Want me to treat you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:42.68,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:45.19,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Then I'll have...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:46.88,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:49.17,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I've never seen anything like this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Princess Crepe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:53.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She's right, I've never seen anything like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:56.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, the price is princess-like, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:58.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Girls are unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:00.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How about something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:02.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How about the Maharajah Crepe-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:02.98,Default-alt,Mei,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:06.41,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Mei wants to have the Princess Crepe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:12.27,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:13.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:15.74,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Do you want to try some, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:17.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then I'll take a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:25.12,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,You took the strawberry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:27.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You said I can try some.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:29.62,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I hate you, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:32.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No! Don't hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:34.97,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Then can we do that together?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:37.97,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Then I'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:39.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're kidding. That's so lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:42.47,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Strawberry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:42.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:44.39,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Maybe it's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:45.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:48.22,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,This is so exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:50.10,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,Choose a frame you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Which one do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:53.74,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:54.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:57.86,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,We'll now take the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:58.43,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:18:59.49,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:01.70,Default,Voice,0,0,0,,Say "Cheese!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:10.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This is really embarrassing, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:13.14,Default-alt,Mei,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san! Make sure you put it on your student ID!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:14.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:22.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:26.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Where've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:27.77,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I was meeting my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:29.73,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What were you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:31.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We were looking for-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:32.67,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:37.65,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:39.87,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:41.18,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:44.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Man, looks like the truth has come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:47.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's just as you imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:50.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Mei-chan's boyfriend turns out to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:52.88,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What happened to Nagisa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:55.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Obviously, I'm breaking up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:59.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The truth is, Mei-chan actually stayed over at my place last night, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:00.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Right, Mei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:05.14,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. I was alone with Okazaki-san, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:11.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Shall we get a move on, Mei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:11.90,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:15.36,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:19.49,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I said wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:33.91,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Why does it have to turn out like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:38.51,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:21:00.79,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,And nothing more?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.79,0:21:04.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I tried to pull off an act thinking we'd make him worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:07.33,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, all for our sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:08.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:12.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But even with all the provocation, he didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:17.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was hoping he'd show his "reliable brother" side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:23.20,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,It looks like he doesn't care about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:25.23,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,That can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.67,0:21:28.46,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But, lying is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.17,0:21:32.42,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Mei-chan, shouldn't you go home soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:34.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You've been absent from school a whole week.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.15,0:21:36.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Your parents must be worried about you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.32,0:21:38.36,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I can't go home leaving things the way they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:40.72,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Not until Onii-chan gets his act together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.14,0:21:43.20,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:47.70,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I want Onii-chan to play soccer again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:52.45,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,If he plays soccer again, maybe he'll return to the way he used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:55.33,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,If possible, he should return to the Soccer Team and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:57.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I think that's difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.39,0:22:02.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You know what happened between Sunohara and the Soccer Team, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.70,0:22:06.18,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,But I think that's our only chance.
