Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:43.20,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'm busy taking care of matters with Sanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.20,0:23:45.60,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I don't have time to worry about Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.16,0:23:48.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Mei-chan, let's think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.81,0:23:56.45,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,He has many good traits but just can't express them well.
